{"type":"message","id":"349985bc","parentId":"717e03fb","timestamp":"2026-05-07T11:00:18.225Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:a1b2c3d4-6666-4000-a000-000000000006 Market Prices Update] Market Prices Update\n\n1. Fetch crypto prices from CoinGecko:\n   URL: https://api.coingecko.com/api/v3/simple/price?ids=bitcoin,ethereum,solana,the-open-network&vs_currencies=usd,vnd&include_24hr_change=true\n   Extract price USD, VND, and 24h change for each coin.\n\n2. Use web search to find current prices for:\n   - Gia vang the gioi (XAU/USD per ounce)\n   - Gia vang SJC Viet Nam (mua vao / ban ra, VND/luong)\n   - Gia dau tho WTI (USD/barrel)\n   - Gia dau Brent (USD/barrel)\n   - Gia xang RON 95 Viet Nam (VND/lit)\n   - Ty gia USD/VND\n\n3. Format the message EXACTLY as follows:\n\n   📊 CAP NHAT GIA — {today's date} {current time}\n   ──────────────────────────────\n\n   💰 CRYPTO\n   ₿ BTC: $PRICE (~VND) | 24h: CHANGE%\n   Ξ ETH: $PRICE (~VND) | 24h: CHANGE%\n   ◎ SOL: $PRICE | 24h: CHANGE%\n   💎 TON: $PRICE | 24h: CHANGE%\n\n   🥇 VANG\n   The gioi (XAU): $PRICE/oz\n   SJC VN: MUA / BAN (VND/luong)\n\n   🛢️ DAU THO\n   WTI: $PRICE/barrel\n   Brent: $PRICE/barrel\n\n   ⛽ XANG DAU VN\n   RON 95: PRICE VND/lit\n\n   💵 TY GIA\n   USD/VND: RATE\n\n   ──────────────────────────────\n\n4. If any price is unavailable, show N/A instead.\n5. Send the formatted message as your response.\nCurrent time: Thursday, May 7th, 2026 - 18:00 (Asia/Saigon) / 2026-05-07 11:00 UTC\n\nReturn your response as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself."}],"timestamp":1778151618219}}
